  "body": "# Bug Report\n## Problem\nIf you enter the name of a chat you have already joined before to the search input (Home screen), then open this chat from suggestions and delete this chat, you will be redirected to Home screen without chat list and search input. \n\n**_After restarting the app chat list and search input will appear again._**\n\n#### Expected behavior\nRedirect to home screen, chat list and search input are shown.\n\n#### Actual behavior\nRedirect to home screen, no chat list and search input.\n\n![ezgif com-resize (6)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/88916336-31124700-d266-11ea-837f-e4073b2c6f42.gif)\n\n### Reproduction\n\n\n1. Join several public chats\n1. Enter the name of one of these chats\n1. Tap chat's name\n1. In opened chat tap 3 dots on the top right\n1. Delete chat -> Delete\n\n### Additional Information\n\n\n* Status version: Nightly 30/07\n* Operating System: Android 8, 10, iOS 13\n\n",
